  "dct_description_sm": [
    "New York City Area Digital Elevation Mode, 1/3 Arc Second (meters) is a raster dataset representing elevations in the New York City area. This layer was clipped from the USGS NED to New York City and its immediate surrounding environment reprojected to show elevation and ground units in meters. The resolution is 1/3 arc second."
